{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861983039,"sessionID":"ses_28660ebcdffe4WXFwNvaCbpCyj","part":{"id":"prt_d799f64b10015jfKAd2T4gLFDw","messageID":"msg_d799f51400017mEEPwmZbmoEzJ","sessionID":"ses_28660ebcdffe4WXFwNvaCbpCyj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-57a5e1683c6c418ab69c5dfa55b725e1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\n2: \n3: ## 模块信息\n4: \n5: - **模块**: `pkg/agentd`\n6: - **语言**: Go\n7: - **规模**: S\n8: - **关联需求**: AR-018\n9: \n10: ## 架构概述\n11: \n12: ### 设计目标\n13: \n14: Agentd 是一个 Kubernetes 控制器，负责监控和管理 AgentCube 中的 Sandbox 资源的空闲状态。当 Sandbox 资源在配置的超时时间内没有活动时，Agentd 自动清理该资源，释放计算资源，防止资源浪费。\n15: \n16: ### 核心组件\n17: \n18: ```\n19: pkg/agentd/\n20: ├── controller.go         # Reconciler 主控制器实现\n21: ├── controller_test.go    # 控制器单元测试\n22: ├── constants.go          # 常量定义（超时时间、注解键等）\n23: └── metrics.go            # Prometheus 指标采集（可选）\n24: ```\n25: \n26: ### 架构原则\n27: \n28: 1. **被动监控**: 通过 Kubernetes Informer 机制被动监听 Sandbox 资源变更\n29: 2. **延迟调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度，避免频繁轮询\n30: 3. **幂等性**: 所有操作都是幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\n31: 4. **最小干扰**: 只在必要时触发清理操作，减少对正常运行中的 Sandbox 的影响\n32: 5. **注解驱动**: 通过注解进行状态通信，与 workload-manager 协同工作\n33: \n34: ## 组件设计\n35: \n36: ### Reconciler 控制器\n37: \n38: #### 数据结构\n39: \n40: ```go\n41: package agentd\n42: \n43: import (\n44:     \"context\"\n45:     \"time\"\n46: \n47:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n48:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n49:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n50:     agentsv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n51: )\n52: \n53: type Reconciler struct {\n54:     client.Client\n55:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n56: }\n57: \n58: type ReconcileResult struct {\n59:     Result reconcile.Result\n60:     Error  error\n61: }\n62: ```\n63: \n64: #### 核心方法\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req reconcile.Request) (reconcile.Result, error)\n68: \n69: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error\n70: ```\n71: \n72: #### 常量定义\n73: \n74: ```go\n75: package agentd\n76: \n77: import \"time\"\n78: \n79: const (\n80:     // SessionExpirationTimeout 定义空闲会话的超时时间\n81:     SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n82: \n83:     // LastActivityAnnotationKey 是用于跟踪最后活动时间的注解键\n84:     LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n85: \n86:     // DefaultRequeueInterval 默认重新调度间隔\n87:     DefaultRequeueInterval = 30 * time.Second\n88: )\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### 控制器注册\n92: \n93: #### SetupWithManager 方法\n94: \n95: ```go\n96: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n97:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n98:         For(&agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n99:         Complete(r)\n100: }\n101: ```\n102: \n103: - 只监听 `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1.Sandbox` 资源\n104: - 使用默认的 Informer 过滤器（监听所有命名空间）\n105: - 不需要额外的 `Owns()` 或 `Watches()` 关联资源\n106: \n107: ## 数据流\n108: \n109: ### 空闲清理流程\n110: \n111: ```\n112: ┌─────────────────┐\n113: │ Sandbox 创建    │\n114: │ (workloadmgr)   │\n115: └────────┬────────┘\n116:          │\n117:          ▼\n118: ┌─────────────────┐\n119: │ 设置注解        │\n120: │ last-activity-  │\n121: │ time = now()    │\n122: └────────┬────────┘\n123:          │\n124:          ▼\n125: ┌─────────────────┐\n126: │ Agentd Reconcile│\n127: │ 触发            │\n128: └────────┬────────┘\n129:          │\n130:          ▼\n131: ┌─────────────────┐\n132: │ 读取注解        │\n133: │ last-activity-  │\n134: │ time            │\n135: └────────┬────────┘\n136:          │\n137:          ▼\n138: ┌─────────────────┐\n139: │ 计算            │\n140: │ expiration =    │\n141: │ activity + 15m  │\n142: └────────┬────────┘\n143:          │\n144:          ▼\n145:     ┌────┴────┐\n146:     │         │\n147:     ▼         ▼\n148: ┌───────┐  ┌───────┐\n149: │已过期? │  │未过期? │\n150: └───┬───┘  └───┬───┘\n151:     │           │\n152:     ▼           ▼\n153: ┌───────┐  ┌───────┐\n154: │删除   │  │Requeue│\n155: │Sandbox│  │After  │\n156: │资源   │  │30s    │\n157: └───────┘  └───────┘\n158: ```\n159: \n160: ### 详细步骤\n161: \n162: 1. **资源变更触发**: 当 Sandbox 资源创建、更新或删除时，Kubernetes Informer 触发 Reconcile\n163: 2. **获取资源**: 从 API Server 获取最新的 Sandbox 资源状态\n164: 3. **检查注解**: 读取 `last-activity-time` 注解的值\n165: 4. **解析时间**: 将注解中的 RFC3339 时间字符串解析为 `time.Time`\n166: 5. **计算超时**: `expirationTime = lastActivity + SessionExpirationTimeout`\n167: 6. **判断状态**:\n168:    - 如果 `now > expirationTime`: 删除 Sandbox 资源\n169:    - 如果 `now <= expirationTime`: 延迟重新调度，等待到超时时间点\n170: 7. **返回结果**: 返回 `reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: duration}` 或错误\n171: \n172: ## 序列图\n173: \n174: ### 空闲清理成功场景\n175: \n176: ```\n177: User          WorkloadManager    K8s API Server    Agentd    Time\n178: │                 │                   │              │         │\n179: │                 │ Create Sandbox    │              │         │\n180: │─────────────────►──────────────────►              │         │\n181: │                 │                   │              │         │\n182: │                 │ Set Annotation    │              │         │\n183: │                 │ (last-activity)   │              │         │\n184: │                 │───────────────────►              │         │\n185: │                 │                   │              │         │\n186: │                 │                   │ Notify       │         │\n187: │                 │                   │─────────────►│         │\n188: │                 │                   │              │         │\n189: │                 │                   │              │ Get     │\n190: │                 │                   │◄─────────────│         │\n191: │                 │                   │              │         │\n192: │                 │                   │              │ Parse   │\n193: │                 │                   │              │ time    │\n194: │                 │                   │              │         │\n195: │                 │                   │              │         │\n196: │                 │                   │              │         │ +15m\n197: │                 │                   │              │         │\n198: │                 │                   │ RequeueAfter  │         │\n199: │                 │                   │─────────────►│         │\n200: │                 │                   │              │         │\n201: │                 │                   │              │         │ (no activity)\n202: │                 │                   │              │         │\n203: │                 │                   │ Notify       │         │\n204: │                 │                   │─────────────►│         │\n205: │                 │                   │              │         │\n206: │                 │                   │              │ Get     │\n207: │                 │                   │◄─────────────│         │\n208: │                 │                   │              │         │\n209: │                 │                   │              │ Check   │\n210: │                 │                   │              │ expired │\n211: │                 │                   │              │         │\n212: │                 │                   │              │         │ (now > expiration)\n213: │                 │                   │              │         │\n214: │                 │                   │ Delete       │         │\n215: │                 │                   │◄─────────────│         │\n216: │                 │                   │              │         │\n217: │                 │ ◄─────────────────│              │         │\n218: │                 │  Sandbox deleted  │              │         │\n219: ```\n220: \n221: ### 资源不存在场景\n222: \n223: ```\n224: User          WorkloadManager    K8s API Server    Agentd\n225: │                 │                   │              │\n226: │                 │                   │ Notify       │\n227: │                 │                   │ (delete)     │\n228: │                 │                   │─────────────►│\n229: │                 │                   │              │\n230: │                 │                   │              │ Get\n231: │                 │                   │◄─────────────│\n232: │                 │                   │              │\n233: │                 │                   │              │ Not found\n234: │                 │                   │              │\n235: │                 │                   │ Return       │\n236: │                 │                   │─────────────►│\n237: │                 │                   │ (no error)   │\n238: ```\n239: \n240: ### 解析错误场景\n241: \n242: ```\n243: User          WorkloadManager    K8s API Server    Agentd\n244: │                 │                   │              │\n245: │                 │                   │ Notify       │\n246: │                 │                   │─────────────►│\n247: │                 │                   │              │\n248: │                 │                   │              │ Get\n249: │                 │                   │◄─────────────│\n250: │                 │                   │              │\n251: │                 │                   │              │ Parse\n252: │                 │                   │              │ (invalid)\n253: │                 │                   │              │\n254: │                 │                   │ RequeueAfter  │\n255: │                 │                   │─────────────►│\n256: │                 │                   │ (30s)        │\n257: │                 │                   │              │\n258: ```\n259: \n260: ## 状态管理\n261: \n262: ### Sandbox 资源生命周期\n263: \n264: ```\n265: ┌──────────┐\n266: │ Pending  │ ───► Set last-activity annotation\n267: └────┬─────┘\n268:      │\n269:      ▼\n270: ┌──────────┐\n271: │ Running  │ ───► Activity detected (update annotation)\n272: └────┬─────┘\n273:      │\n274:      ▼\n275: ┌──────────┐\n276: │ Idle     │ ───► No activity for >15m\n277: └────┬─────┘\n278:      │\n279:      ▼\n280: ┌──────────┐\n281: │ Deleted  │ ───► Removed by Agentd\n282: └──────────┘\n283: ```\n284: \n285: ### 注解管理\n286: \n287: #### 设置注解 (由 workload-manager)\n288: \n289: ```go\n290: sandbox.SetAnnotations(map[string]string{\n291:     \"last-activity-time\": time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n292: })\n293: ```\n294: \n295: #### 读取注解 (由 agentd)\n296: \n297: ```go\n298: lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n299: if exists && lastActivityStr != \"\" {\n300:     lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n301:     // 处理 lastActivity\n302: }\n303: ```\n304: \n305: ### 状态转换条件\n306: \n307: | 当前状态 | 转换条件 | 下一状态 |\n308: |---------|---------|---------|\n309: | Pending | Annotation 设置 | Running |\n310: | Running | Annotation 更新 | Running (reset timer) |\n311: | Running | 无活动 > 15m | Deleted |\n312: | Running | 手动删除 | Deleted |\n313: \n314: ## 并发模型\n315: \n316: ### Informer 机制\n317: \n318: Agentd 使用 controller-runtime 的 Informer 机制，该机制提供了以下并发保证：\n319: \n320: 1. **缓存一致性**: Informer 维护本地缓存，通过 List-Watch 机制与 API Server 同步\n321: 2. **事件去重**: 相同资源的事件会被去重，避免重复处理\n322: 3. **顺序处理**: 同一资源的事件按时间顺序处理\n323: 4. **工作队列**: 使用工作队列实现异步处理，支持并发度配置\n324: \n325: ### Reconcile 线程模型\n326: \n327: ```go\n328: // controller-runtime 默认配置\n329: // 可以通过 MaxConcurrentReconciles 调整并发度\n330: return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n331:     For(&agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n332:     WithOptions(controller.Options{MaxConcurrentReconciles: 10}).\n333:     Complete(r)\n334: ```\n335: \n336: ### 并发安全考虑\n337: \n338: 1. **只读操作**: Reconcile 主要是只读操作（Get、List），不需要额外的锁\n339: 2. **幂等删除**: Delete 操作是幂等的，重复执行不会产生副作用\n340: 3. **状态检查**: 在删除前检查资源是否存在，避免竞争条件\n341: 4. **延迟重试**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 而不是立即重试，减少 API Server 压力\n342: \n343: ## 错误处理\n344: \n345: ### 错误分类\n346: \n347: | 错误类型 | 处理策略 | 示例 |\n348: |---------|---------|------|\n349: | 资源不存在 | 返回无错误 | `IsNotFound(err)` |\n350: | 解析错误 | 延迟重试 | 无效的 RFC3339 时间 |\n351: | API 错误 | 返回错误触发重试 | 网络超时、权限错误 |\n352: | 删除错误 | 返回错误触发重试 | 资源被锁定 |\n353: \n354: ### 错误处理策略\n355: \n356: ```go\n357: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req reconcile.Request) (reconcile.Result, error) {\n358:     // 1. 获取资源\n359:     sandbox := &agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox{}\n360:     if err := r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox); err != nil {\n361:         if apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n362:             // 资源已删除，无需处理\n363:             return reconcile.Result{}, nil\n364:         }\n365:         // 其他错误返回，触发重试\n366:         return reconcile.Result{}, err\n367:     }\n368: \n369:     // 2. 读取注解\n370:     lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n371:     if !exists || lastActivityStr == \"\" {\n372:         // 没有注解，无需处理\n373:         return reconcile.Result{}, nil\n374:     }\n375: \n376:     // 3. 解析时间\n377:     lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n378:     if err != nil {\n379:         // 解析错误，延迟重试\n380:         return reconcile.Result{\n381:             RequeueAfter: DefaultRequeueInterval,\n382:         }, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse last activity time: %w\", err)\n383:     }\n384: \n385:     // 4. 检查是否过期\n386:     expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n387:     if time.Now().After(expirationTime) {\n388:         // 已过期，删除资源\n389:         if err := r.Delete(ctx, sandbox); err != nil {\n390:             if !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n391:                 // 删除失败，返回错误触发重试\n392:                 return reconcile.Result{}, err\n393:             }\n394:             // 资源已不存在，无需处理\n395:         }\n396:         return reconcile.Result{}, nil\n397:     }\n398: \n399:     // 5. 未过期，延迟重新调度\n400:     return reconcile.Result{\n401:         RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime),\n402:     }, nil\n403: }\n404: ```\n405: \n406: ### 不可恢复错误\n407: \n408: 以下错误被认为是不可恢复的，会导致控制器 panic 或停止：\n409: \n410: 1. **配置错误**: 环境变量配置错误\n411: 2. **连接失败**: 无法连接到 Kubernetes API Server\n412: 3. **权限错误**: 缺少必要的 RBAC 权限\n413: \n414: 这些错误通常在控制器启动时检查，不会在 Reconcile 中出现。\n415: \n416: ## API 契约\n417: \n418: ### Watched Resources\n419: \n420: | API Group | Version | Kind | Watch Type | Trigger |\n421: |-----------|---------|------|------------|---------|\n422: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Primary | Create, Update, Delete |\n423: \n424: ### Reconcile Request\n425: \n426: ```go\n427: type reconcile.Request struct {\n428:     NamespacedName types.NamespacedName\n429: }\n430: \n431: type NamespacedName struct {\n432:     Namespace string\n433:     Name      string\n434: }\n435: ```\n436: \n437: ### Reconcile Result\n438: \n439: ```go\n440: type reconcile.Result struct {\n441:     Requeue      bool\n442:     RequeueAfter time.Duration\n443: }\n444: ```\n445: \n446: - `Requeue: true`: 立即重新调度\n447: - `RequeueAfter > 0`: 延迟指定时间后重新调度\n448: - 默认: 不重新调度\n449: \n450: ### 必需的 RBAC 权限\n451: \n452: ```yaml\n453: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n454: kind: ClusterRole\n455: metadata:\n456:   name: agentd\n457: rules:\n458:   - apiGroups:\n459:       - agents.x-k8s.io\n460:     resources:\n461:       - sandboxes\n462:     verbs:\n463:       - get\n464:       - list\n465:       - watch\n466:       - delete\n467:   - apiGroups:\n468:       - agents.x-k8s.io\n469:     resources:\n470:       - sandboxes/status\n471:     verbs:\n472:       - get\n473: ```\n474: \n475: ## 依赖项\n476: \n477: | 依赖 | 版本 | 用途 |\n478: |------|------|------|\n479: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.17.x | Kubernetes 控制器框架 |\n480: | `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | v1alpha1 | Sandbox CRD 类型定义 |\n481: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.29.x | Kubernetes API 基础类型 |\n482: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | v0.29.x | 核心资源类型 |\n483: \n484: ## 测试策略\n485: \n486: ### 单元测试\n487: \n488: 1. **Reconcile 逻辑测试**:\n489:    - 资源不存在场景\n490:    - 注解缺失场景\n491:    - 未过期场景（验证 RequeueAfter 时间）\n492:    - 已过期场景（验证删除操作）\n493: \n494: 2. **时间解析测试**:\n495:    - 有效的 RFC3339 格式\n496:    - 无效的时间格式\n497:    - 边界时间值\n498: \n499: 3. **并发测试**:\n500:    - 多个并发 Reconcile 调用\n501:    - 资源竞争场景\n502: \n503: ### 集成测试\n504: \n505: 1. **端到端测试**:\n506:    - 创建 Sandbox → 等待超时 → 验证删除\n507:    - 更新注解 → 验证重置计时器\n508:    - 手动删除 → 验证无错误\n509: \n510: 2. **性能测试**:\n511:    - 大量 Sandbox 资源下的性能表现\n512:    - 内存使用和 CPU 消耗\n513: \n514: 3. **错误恢复测试**:\n515:    - API Server 不可达\n516:    - 网络分区\n517:    - 权限不足\n518: \n519: ## 部署配置\n520: \n521: ### 环境变量\n522: \n523: | 变量 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n524: |------|------|--------|------|\n525: | `SESSION_TIMEOUT` | duration | `15m` | 空闲会话超时时间 |\n526: | `REQUEUE_INTERVAL` | duration | `30s` | 解析错误时的重试间隔 |\n527: | `NAMESPACE` | string | `\"\"` | 监听的命名空间（空表示所有命名空间） |\n528: \n529: ### 命令行参数\n530: \n531: ```bash\n532: # 运行 agentd\n533: ./agentd \\\n534:   --session-timeout=15m \\\n535:   --requeue-interval=30s \\\n536:   --metrics-bind-address=:8080 \\\n537:   --leader-elect\n538: ```\n539: \n540: ### Kubernetes Deployment\n541: \n542: ```yaml\n543: apiVersion: apps/v1\n544: kind: Deployment\n545: metadata:\n546:   name: agentd\n547:   namespace: agentcube\n548: spec:\n549:   replicas: 2\n550:   selector:\n551:     matchLabels:\n552:       app: agentd\n553:   template:\n554:     metadata:\n555:       labels:\n556:         app: agentd\n557:     spec:\n558:       containers:\n559:       - name: agentd\n560:         image: volcano-sh/agentcube-agentd:latest\n561:         args:\n562:           - --session-timeout=15m\n563:           - --requeue-interval=30s\n564:           - --leader-elect\n565:         resources:\n566:           requests:\n567:             cpu: 100m\n568:             memory: 128Mi\n569:           limits:\n570:             cpu: 500m\n571:             memory: 256Mi\n572: ```\n573: \n574: ## 监控指标\n575: \n576: ### Prometheus 指标（可选）\n577: \n578: | 指标名称 | 类型 | 标签 | 说明 |\n579: |---------|------|------|------|\n580: | `agentd_reconcile_total` | Counter | result | Reconcile 调用总数 |\n581: | `agentd_reconcile_duration` | Histogram | | Reconcile 执行时间 |\n582: | `agentd_sandbox_deleted_total` | Counter | reason | 删除的 Sandbox 总数 |\n583: | `agentd_sandbox_active` | Gauge | namespace | 当前活跃的 Sandbox 数量 |\n584: \n585: ### 日志记录\n586: \n587: 使用 klog 进行日志记录：\n588: \n589: ```go\n590: klog.InfoS(\"Sandbox is idle and will be deleted\",\n591:     \"namespace\", req.Namespace,\n592:     \"name\", req.Name,\n593:     \"idleDuration\", time.Since(lastActivity),\n594: )\n595: \n596: klog.ErrorS(err, \"Failed to delete sandbox\",\n597:     \"namespace\", req.Namespace,\n598:     \"name\", req.Name,\n599: )\n600: ```\n601: \n602: ## 扩展性考虑\n603: \n604: ### 自定义超时时间\n605: \n606: 支持从 Sandbox CRD 的 `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` 注解读取自定义超时时间：\n607: \n608: ```go\n609: idleTimeoutStr := sandbox.Annotations[\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"]\n610: if idleTimeoutStr != \"\" {\n611:     if timeout, err := time.ParseDuration(idleTimeoutStr); err == nil {\n612:         expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(timeout)\n613:     }\n614: }\n615: ```\n616: \n617: ### 批量清理优化\n618: \n619: 支持批量查询和清理过期的 Sandbox：\n620: \n621: ```go\n622: func (r *Reconciler) cleanupExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context) error {\n623:     sandboxes := &agentsv1alpha1.SandboxList{}\n624:     if err := r.List(ctx, sandboxes); err != nil {\n625:         return err\n626:     }\n627: \n628:     for _, sb := range sandboxes.Items {\n629:         if r.isExpired(&sb) {\n630:             r.Delete(ctx, &sb)\n631:         }\n632:     }\n633:     return nil\n634: }\n635: ```\n636: \n637: ### 优雅关闭\n638: \n639: 实现优雅关闭逻辑，确保在控制器关闭时完成正在处理的 Reconcile：\n640: \n641: ```go\n642: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(cfg, ctrl.Options{\n643:     LeaderElection:          true,\n644:     LeaderElectionID:       \"agentd-leader\",\n645:     LeaderElectionNamespace: \"agentcube\",\n646: })\n647: \n648: defer func() {\n649:     ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), 30*time.Second)\n650:     defer cancel()\n651:     mgr.Shutdown(ctx)\n652: }()\n653: ```\n654: \n655: ## 安全考虑\n656: \n657: ### RBAC 权限\n658: \n659: 最小权限原则：只授予必要的权限\n660: \n661: ```yaml\n662: rules:\n663:   - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n664:     resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n665:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n666: ```\n667: \n668: ### 审计日志\n669: \n670: 记录所有删除操作，便于审计：\n671: \n672: ```go\n673: klog.InfoS(\"Sandbox deleted due to inactivity\",\n674:     \"namespace\", sandbox.Namespace,\n675:     \"name\", sandbox.Name,\n676:     \"uid\", sandbox.UID,\n677:     \"idleDuration\", time.Since(lastActivity),\n678:     \"deletedAt\", time.Now(),\n679: )\n680: ```\n681: \n682: ### 资源保护\n683: \n684: 防止误删重要资源：\n685: \n686: 1. **标签过滤**: 只删除带有特定标签的 Sandbox\n687: 2. **命名空间隔离**: 支持配置允许清理的命名空间\n688: 3. **保护注解**: 支持设置保护注解防止被删除\n689: \n690: ```go\n691: if sandbox.Annotations[\"agentcube/protected\"] == \"true\" {\n692:     return reconcile.Result{}, nil\n693: }\n694: ```\n695: \n696: ## 与其他组件的交互\n697: \n698: ### 与 workload-manager 的交互\n699: \n700: | workload-manager → agentd | 说明 |\n701: |--------------------------|------|\n702: | 设置 `last-activity-time` 注解 | 更新活动时间 |\n703: | 设置 `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` 注解 | 配置自定义超时 |\n704: | 创建 Sandbox 资源 | 触发 agentd 监控 |\n705: \n706: ### 与 Agent Sandbox API 的交互\n707: \n708: Agentd 只读取 Sandbox 资源的元数据（annotations），不修改资源的 spec 或 status，确保与 Agent Sandbox API 的兼容性。\n709: \n710: ## 故障处理\n711: \n712: ### 常见故障场景\n713: \n714: 1. **API Server 不可达**:\n715:    - 现象: Reconcile 失败，错误日志频繁\n716:    - 处理: controller-runtime 自动重试，指数退避\n717:    - 恢复: API Server 恢复后自动继续处理\n718: \n719: 2. **注解格式错误**:\n720:    - 现象: 解析失败，延迟 30 秒重试\n721:    - 处理: 日志记录错误，不中断服务\n722:    - 恢复: workload-manager 修正注解格式后自动恢复\n723: \n724: 3. **资源删除失败**:\n725:    - 现象: 删除命令失败，资源仍存在\n726:    - 处理: 返回错误触发重试\n727:    - 恢复: 锁定解除后自动重试成功\n728: \n729: 4. **资源竞争**:\n730:    - 现象: 同时有多个进程尝试删除同一资源\n731:    - 处理: Delete 操作幂等，只第一次成功\n732:    - 恢复: 自动继续处理\n733: \n734: ### 健康检查\n735: \n736: 实现健康检查端点：\n737: \n738: ```go\n739: // +kubebuilder:webhook:path=/healthz,verbs=get;post,admissionReviewVersions=v1\n740: func (r *Reconciler) Healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, req *http.Request) {\n741:     if err := r.Ping(); err != nil {\n742:         w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n743:         return\n744:     }\n745:     w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n746: }\n747: ```\n748: \n749: ### 就绪检查\n750: \n751: 实现就绪检查端点：\n752: \n753: ```go\n754: // +kubebuilder:webhook:path=/readyz,verbs=get;post,admissionReviewVersions=v1\n755: func (r *Reconciler) Readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, req *http.Request) {\n756:     if !r.cacheSynced() {\n757:         w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n758:         return\n759:     }\n760:     w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n761: }\n762: ```\n763: \n764: ## 性能优化\n765: \n766: ### 批量操作\n767: \n768: 对于大规模集群，使用 List 操作代替单个 Get：\n769: \n770: ```go\n771: func (r *Reconciler) reconcileAll(ctx context.Context) (reconcile.Result, error) {\n772:     sandboxes := &agentsv1alpha1.SandboxList{}\n773:     if err := r.List(ctx, sandboxes); err != nil {\n774:         return reconcile.Result{}, err\n775:     }\n776: \n777:     now := time.Now()\n778:     for _, sb := range sandboxes.Items {\n779:         if r.shouldCleanup(&sb, now) {\n780:             r.Delete(ctx, &sb)\n781:         }\n782:     }\n783: \n784:     return reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: 1 * time.Minute}, nil\n785: }\n786: ```\n787: \n788: ### 索引优化\n789: \n790: 为注解字段创建索引，加速查询：\n791: \n792: ```go\n793: // 在 SetupWithManager 中添加\n794: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n795:     if err := mgr.GetFieldIndexer().IndexField(\n796:         context.Background(),\n797:         &agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox{},\n798:         \"metadata.annotations.last-activity-time\",\n799:         func(rawObj client.Object) []string {\n800:             sb := rawObj.(*agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox)\n801:             if sb.Annotations == nil {\n802:                 return nil\n803:             }\n804:             return []string{sb.Annotations[LastActivityAnnotationKey]}\n805:         },\n806:     ); err != nil {\n807:         return err\n808:     }\n809: \n810:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n811:         For(&agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n812:         Complete(r)\n813: }\n814: ```\n815: \n816: ### 内存优化\n817: \n818: 1. **限制缓存大小**: 配置 Informer 的缓存大小限制\n819: 2. **选择性监听**: 只监听必要的命名空间\n820: 3. **事件过滤**: 使用 Predicates 过滤不相关的事件\n821: \n822: ## 二进制入口点\n823: \n824: ### cmd/agentd/main.go\n825: \n826: ```go\n827: package main\n828: \n829: import (\n830:     \"context\"\n831:     \"flag\"\n832:     \"os\"\n833: \n834:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n835:     utilruntime \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime\"\n836:     clientgoscheme \"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/scheme\"\n837:     _ \"k8s.io/client-go/plugin/pkg/client/auth\"\n838: \n839:     agentsv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n840:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/healthz\"\n841:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/log/zap\"\n842:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager\"\n843:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager/signals\"\n844:     ctrl \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n845: \n846:     agentd \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n847: )\n848: \n849: var (\n850:     scheme   = runtime.NewScheme()\n851:     setupLog = ctrl.Log.WithName(\"setup\")\n852: )\n853: \n854: func init() {\n855:     utilruntime.Must(clientgoscheme.AddToScheme(scheme))\n856:     utilruntime.Must(agentsv1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme))\n857: }\n858: \n859: func main() {\n860:     var metricsAddr string\n861:     var enableLeaderElection bool\n862:     var probeAddr string\n863: \n864:     flag.StringVar(&metricsAddr, \"metrics-bind-address\", \":8080\", \"The address the metric endpoint binds to.\")\n865:     flag.StringVar(&probeAddr, \"health-probe-bind-address\", \":8081\", \"The address the probe endpoint binds to.\")\n866:     flag.BoolVar(&enableLeaderElection, \"leader-elect\", false,\n867:         \"Enable leader election for controller manager. \"+\n868:             \"Enabling this will ensure there is only one active controller manager.\")\n869: \n870:     opts := zap.Options{\n871:         Development: true,\n872:     }\n873:     opts.BindFlags(flag.CommandLine)\n874:     flag.Parse()\n875: \n876:     ctrl.SetLogger(zap.New(zap.UseFlagOptions(&opts)))\n877: \n878:     mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n879:         Scheme:                 scheme,\n880:         MetricsBindAddress:     metricsAddr,\n881:         Port:                   9443,\n882:         HealthProbeBindAddress: probeAddr,\n883:         LeaderElection:         enableLeaderElection,\n884:         LeaderElectionID:       \"agentd-leader\",\n885:     })\n886:     if err != nil {\n887:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to start manager\")\n888:         os.Exit(1)\n889:     }\n890: \n891:     if err = (&agentd.Reconciler{\n892:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n893:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n894:     }).SetupWithManager(mgr); err != nil {\n895:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to create controller\", \"controller\", \"Agentd\")\n896:         os.Exit(1)\n897:     }\n898: \n899:     if err := mgr.AddHealthzCheck(\"healthz\", healthz.Ping); err != nil {\n900:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to set up health check\")\n901:         os.Exit(1)\n902:     }\n903: \n904:     if err := mgr.AddReadyzCheck(\"readyz\", healthz.Ping); err != nil {\n905:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to set up ready check\")\n906:         os.Exit(1)\n907:     }\n908: \n909:     setupLog.Info(\"starting manager\")\n910:     if err := mgr.Start(signals.SetupSignalHandler()); err != nil {\n911:         setupLog.Error(err, \"problem running manager\")\n912:         os.Exit(1)\n913:     }\n914: }\n915: ```\n916: \n917: ## 相关 workload-manager 常量\n918: \n919: 从 `pkg/workloadmanager` 导入的常量（仅用于理解上下文，不由 agentd 使用）：\n920: \n921: ```go\n922: const (\n923:     IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n924:     LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n925: )\n926: ```\n927: \n928: **说明**:\n929: - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey`: 由 workload-manager 设置，用于配置自定义超时时间（可选）\n930: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey`: 由 workload-manager 设置，agentd 读取此注解判断是否过期\n931: \n932: ## 总结\n933: \n934: Agentd 是一个轻量级的 Kubernetes 控制器，通过监听 Sandbox 资源的 `last-activity-time` 注解来实现空闲清理功能。其核心设计包括：\n935: \n936: 1. **被动监控**: 使用 Informer 机制，高效监听资源变更\n937: 2. **精确调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度\n938: 3. **幂等操作**: 所有操作都是幂等的，安全可靠\n939: 4. **最小权限**: 遵循最小权限原则，只授予必要的 RBAC 权限\n940: 5. **可观测性**: 支持日志、指标和健康检查\n941: 6. **高可用**: 支持多副本部署和 Leader 选举\n942: \n943: 通过这些设计，Agentd 能够高效、可靠地清理空闲的 Sandbox 资源，释放计算资源，同时最小化对正常运行中的工作负载的影响。\n\n(End of file - total 943 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\n\n## 模块信息\n\n- **模块**: `pkg/agentd`\n- **语言**: Go\n- **规模**: S\n- **关联需求**: AR-018\n\n## 架构概述\n\n### 设计目标\n\nAgentd 是一个 Kubernetes 控制器，负责监控和管理 AgentCube 中的 Sandbox 资源的空闲状态。当 Sandbox 资源在配置的超时时间内没有活动时，Agentd 自动清理该资源，释放计算资源，防止资源浪费。\n\n### 核心组件\n\n```\npkg/agentd/\n├── controller.go         # Reconciler 主控制器实现","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/design.md","time":{"start":1775861983017,"end":1775861983036}}}}
